    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-oriented example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe has undergone preventative reinforcement. The suspension is upgraded with Bilstein dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary poise and communicative steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and rod bearing inspections\u2014confirm this vehicle is tuned for high-revving performance and peak lateral acceleration.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
