      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and refined aesthetics. Meticulously maintained, the exterior boasts a deep shine with only minor cosmetic imperfections typical of careful road use. Inside, you will find a smoke-free environment where the premium upholstery remains supple and every electronic feature\u2014from the crisp sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has followed a strict service schedule, resulting in a smooth transmission and a responsive, quiet engine. Whether you are looking for a dependable commuter or a comfortable weekend traveler, this car offers a turnkey experience with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 36800.0,
